column6: DOOM PART 5 The Fantastic Four have been granted clearance to retaliate against Victor Van Damme. Now, in command of a small monarchy in the middle of Europe and in control of a secret weapon, the Four may have met their match!
column8: | letterer:Chris Eliopoulos | writer:Warren Ellis | inker:Wade von Grawbadger | penciller (cover):Stuart Immonen | colorist:Dave Stewart
